title: WildStar Beta Leak
description:
The short story. My guild registered aproxx. 100+ emails for the WildStar beta event. After getting enough invites to hand out to those who actually want in, our guild master started selling the invites. Everyone in our guild was banned and will no longer be allowed into the beta.

So, why should I continue to hold onto this footage?

The file is VERY (33gb) large. The quality is 100% top notch, a near of a direct copy of my screen as I could make. I hope you enjoy it.
